data.description: This charming single-story home, with its cozy design and thoughtful layout, offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With just over 1200 square feet of living space, it strikes an ideal balance between spaciousness and easy maintenance.    Upon entering, you are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the living room, dining space, and kitchen, creating a perfect hub for family gatherings and entertaining. Natural light pours in through large windows, creating a bright and airy ambiance that enhances the sense of space.    The three well-appointed bedrooms are generously sized and provide ample privacy for each member of the household. The master suite features an en-suite bathroom, offering a retreat-like experience. The other two bedrooms share a conveniently located bathroom, perfect for family members or guests.    Cozy backyard, providing outdoor spaces for relaxation and play. The manageable yard size makes maintenance a breeze, allowing more time for enjoying the lovely surroundings.    This home offers a serene retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life while still being conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers. Its single-story design makes it accessible and accommodating for all generations.
